    <item>
      <title>卡梅伦告诉美国切断乌克兰将是送给普京和习近平的礼物</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-07/uk-s-cameron-urges-us-congress-to-pass-ukraine-funding-package</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国外交大臣戴维·卡梅伦敦促美国国会批准数十亿美元支持乌克兰对俄战争，称如果不这样做，可能会助长俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京的气焰。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-07/uk-s-cameron-urges-us-congress-to-pass-ukraine-funding-package</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 16:32:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>普京罕见访问海湾后承诺加强俄罗斯与伊朗关系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-07/putin-pledges-closer-russia-iran-ties-after-rare-visit-to-gulf</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京(Vladimir Putin)和伊朗总统易卜拉欣·莱西(Ebrahim Raisi)周四誓言要深化关系，此前一天，俄罗斯领导人罕见地访问了沙特阿拉伯和阿拉伯联合酋长国。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-07/putin-pledges-closer-russia-iran-ties-after-rare-visit-to-gulf</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 16:13:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登弹劾调查将于下周众议院投票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-07/biden-impeachment-inquiry-set-for-house-vote-next-week</link>
      <description><![CDATA[众议院共和党人周四迈出了一步，正式授权对总统乔·拜登进行与其家族商业交易有关的弹劾调查。]]></description>
